tde-refresh-trinity (1.2) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Recommend xdg-user-dirs-gtk (creates the standard XDG user directories),
    gnuplot-nox (plotting backend for qalculate/kmplot), tdmtheme-trinity
    (TDM login theme manager) and desktop-base-trinity (default desktop
    artwork/branding).

 -- yjlion <yjlion@gmail.com>  Tue, 14 Jul 2026 23:57:12 -0400

tde-refresh-trinity (1.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Restructure dependencies for a more granular, less forceful install:
    - Drop the monolithic module Depends: tdeadmin-trinity,
      tdegraphics-trinity, tdemultimedia-trinity, tdenetwork-trinity,
      tdepim-trinity and tdeutils-trinity.
    - Pull in a curated set of the individual applications and TDEIO/file
      plugins those modules contained as Recommends instead, so users can
      drop individual apps without fighting module-level dependencies.
    - Move tdeedu-trinity, tdeio-apt-trinity and synaptic-trinity to
      Suggests.

 -- yjlion <yjlion@gmail.com>  Tue, 14 Jul 2026 22:04:28 -0400

